citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:40 am on
06/29/2016.
APHIS VMO knocked on the door, rang both doorbells and called the licensee's telephone number. The VMO was
unable to leave a message as the voicemail box was full. The VMO waited 30 minutes before departing the facility.
